            <title>[SPARK-42112] Add null check before `ContinuousWriteRDD#compute` method close dataWriter</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-42112</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Run&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;mvn clean test -pl sql/core -Dtest=none -DwildcardSuites=org.apache.spark.sql.streaming.continuous.ContinuousSuite -am&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;NPE exists in the test log&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
